    "The methods are applicable to a wide variety of data types and objects.",
    "This includes point cloud data in Euclidean spaces, categorical data, or the analysis of images and functions.",
    "TDA is backed by explainable theory but lacks the learning ability and other practical aspects of deep neural networks.",
    "Conversely, neural networks suffer from the need for large training datasets and billions of tunable parameters.",
    "Due to these aspects, integration of TDA with deep neural networks poses a number of challenges."
